//      <o.7..7> MODS
//        <0=> 0: UserMode = User Mode (Calculate every data written to the CRC_IN register)
//        <1=> 1: AutoMode = Auto Mode (Calculate till CRC_SADR == CRC_EADR)
//    </combo>
//  </item>
//  


